Create Slave
SyncState *

# jay.kruer@sifive.com

MaildirStore jay.kruer@sifive.com-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/jay.kruer@sifive.com/
Inbox ~/mail/jay.kruer@sifive.com/INBOX

IMAPStore jay.kruer@sifive.com-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User jay.kruer@sifive.com
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
SSLType IMAPS
PassCmd "pass show sifive/mbsync"

Channel jay.kruer@sifive.com
Master :jay.kruer@sifive.com-remote:
Slave :jay.kruer@sifive.com-local:
Patterns *
Sync PullNew PullFlags

